                <head>[Translation.]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington, D. C.,</hi>
                        </placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1903-11-10">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 10, 1903</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p rend="flushleft">
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Glass</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Marblehead, Panama:</hi>
                </p>
                <p>Reported that the British steamers at Buenaventura were not detained. Did they
                    leave with Colombian troops aboard?</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Moody.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
